00:41:17,934 --> 00:41:20,479
都是由於你對生化冷凍抗體過敏導致的
are an allergic reaction to the cytoprethaline.

658
00:41:20,562 --> 00:41:22,230
這種藥物是在生化冷凍休眠過程中
It's a drug we inject to keep ice crystals

659
00:41:22,314 --> 00:41:23,732
防止細胞體結冰用的
from forming in your cells during cryo sleep.

660
00:41:23,815 --> 00:41:26,443
發病率大概是50000之一
It occurs in about one in every 50,000 or so.

661
00:41:26,526 --> 00:41:30,530
所以，每次我從生化冷凍休眠中醒來，我都不能呼吸
So I won't be able to breathe every time I wake up from cryo sleep.

662
00:41:31,531 --> 00:41:34,201
你的過敏源濃度結果還沒出來
The intensity of your allergy is still undetermined.

663
00:41:34,284 --> 00:41:36,328
幾個小時之內就會有確定結果
I'll know more in a few hours.

664
00:41:37,746 --> 00:41:40,749
我希望你能夠放鬆心情，今天剩下的時間都好好休息
I want you to take it real easy the rest of the day today.

665
00:41:40,832 --> 00:41:42,334
遵命，長官
Yes, sir.

666
00:41:47,130 --> 00:41:48,340
謝謝
Thanks.

667
00:41:53,386 --> 00:41:54,888
<font color="#D900D9">(Sighs)</font>

668
00:41:58,892 --> 00:42:03,522
<font color="#D900D9">(Sounds of distant combat)</font>

669
00:42:04,523 --> 00:42:05,774
你好，兄弟
Hey, bro.

670
00:42:08,193 --> 00:42:12,072
我在安德西亞，再有一次任務就回家了
I'm on Andesia. It's a jump away from home.

671
00:42:12,155 --> 00:42:14,074
這是第，嗯…
It's day, uh...

672
00:42:16,785 --> 00:42:18,703
496天
496.

673
00:42:20,872 --> 00:42:23,041
很抱歉昨天我沒上線
I'm sorry I didn't com yesterday.

674
00:42:25,210 --> 00:42:28,338
沒法上來，因為我們一場戰鬥打了7個小時
Couldn't. We got pinned in a firefight for seven hours.

675
00:42:33,552 --> 00:42:37,013
嗯，我想我大概能消滅了一打兒叛軍吧
Uh, I must have killed a dozen looies, though.

676
00:42:38,890 --> 00:42:40,475
媽媽會很開心的
Mom would be proud.

677
00:42:43,103 --> 00:42:45,313
我在這邊做的很好
I'm doing real good work here.

678
00:42:45,397 --> 00:42:47,023
我們幹的不錯
We're doing a good thing.

679
00:42:52,112 --> 00:42:53,780
裡奇沒能挺過來
Rich didn't make it.

680
00:42:53,863 --> 00:42:55,448
就是咱們家鄉的那個裡奇
You remember Rich from back home.

681
00:42:59,286 --> 00:43:01,705
他就在我身邊，然後…
He was right there next to me and then...

682
00:43:03,123 --> 00:43:05,458
他沒能熬過來
he wasn't.

683
00:43:05,542 --> 00:43:08,295
一顆榴彈把他炸向4個不同的方向
A pineapple sent him flying in four different directions.

684
00:43:16,636 --> 00:43:19,264
為了裡奇，我把頭髮都剃了
I had to shave it all off for Rich.

685
00:43:20,473 --> 00:43:22,225
他說這樣可以讓我看起來更像個硬漢
He said it'd make me look tougher.

686
00:43:24,978 --> 00:43:26,354
不管怎樣，呃…
Anyways, uh...

687
00:43:28,523 --> 00:43:30,567
我要走了，兄弟
I got to go, bro.

688
00:43:32,068 --> 00:43:33,820
我等不及要回家了
I can't wait to get home.

689
00:43:33,903 --> 00:43:35,530
咱們到時候見，凱德蒙通話完畢
I'll see you. Cadmon out.

690
00:43:35,614 --> 00:43:37,574
<font color="#D900D9">(touchscreen beeps)</font>

691
00:43:37,657 --> 00:43:38,742
你在做什麼呢？
What are you doing?

692
00:43:43,163 --> 00:43:45,165
你何必這樣折磨自己呢？
Why do you torment yourself with these?

693
00:43:50,170 --> 00:43:51,588
你沒事吧？
Are you okay?

694
00:43:55,884 --> 00:43:56,968
我本該更好的
<font color="#808080">CHYLER:</font> Whoa!

695
00:43:57,052 --> 00:43:58,762
休醫生怎麼說的？
<font color="#808080">THOMAS:</font> I've been better.

696
00:43:57,052 --> 00:43:58,762
What did Dr. Hughes say?

697
00:43:58,845 --> 00:44:00,764
他說沒事
That it's nothing.

698
00:44:00,847 --> 00:44:02,724
真的？
Really?

699
00:44:11,399 --> 00:44:12,859
今天我們贏了
You know, we won today.

700
00:44:13,860 --> 00:44:15,654
你的戰術奏效了
Your strategy worked.

701
00:44:17,405 --> 00:44:20,367
我只是當了回隊長罷了
That's just me being a leader.

702
00:44:23,870 --> 00:44:25,080
拉斯基，醒醒
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> <font color="#D900D9">(on video screen)</font> Lasky, wake up.

703
00:44:25,163 --> 00:44:27,165
噢，嘿，凱勒
Oh, hey, Chyler.

704
00:44:27,248 --> 00:44:29,000
噢，什麼事，小蘇？
Oh. What's up, Sully?

705
00:44:29,084 --> 00:44:31,002
來我這兒，給你們看樣東西
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Get in here. You guys gotta see this.

706
00:44:35,632 --> 00:44:37,092
你看上去糟透了
<font color="#808080">WALTER:</font> You look like crap.

707
00:44:37,175 --> 00:44:43,515
敬請觀賞我拼湊出來的絕密非官方情報吧
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> So feast your eyes on Grade-A

708
00:44:40,178 --> 00:44:43,515
classified nonlisted intelligence vids I pieced together.

709
00:44:43,598 --> 00:44:47,560
拼這東西太累人了，但很值啊
Super pain in the ass to do, but so worth it.

710
00:44:47,644 --> 00:44:49,145
<font color="#D900D9">(gunfire, shouting)</font>

711
00:44:49,229 --> 00:44:51,147
這比最高機密還機密啊
<font color="#808080">DIMAH:</font> This is beyond top secret.

712
00:44:51,231 --> 00:44:53,525
我從沒看到過如此複雜的加密影像
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> I've never seen something encrypted so hard,

713
00:44:53,608 --> 00:44:55,276
但我還是破解了
but I cracked it.

714
00:44:56,695 --> 00:44:57,737
太瘋狂了，不是麼？
<font color="#808080">JJ:</font> Wow.

715
00:44:57,821 --> 00:44:58,822
是啊
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> It's crazy, huh?

716
00:44:58,905 --> 00:45:00,448
目標已鎖定
<font color="#808080">JJ:</font> Yeah.

717
00:44:58,905 --> 00:45:00,448
MAN <font color="#D900D9">(on video)</font>: Target located.

718
00:45:00,532 --> 00:45:02,826
等下，等下，馬上就是最精彩的部分了
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Wait, wait, wait. Now here comes the best part.

719
00:45:02,909 --> 00:45:04,160
看這裡，看他的手
Wait, watch this. Watch his hand.

720
00:45:04,244 --> 00:45:05,745
目標已捕獲
<font color="#808080">MAN:</font> Target acquired!

721
00:45:05,829 --> 00:45:08,540
不，別！他們來了！他們來了！
No, no! They're coming! They're coming!

722
00:45:08,623 --> 00:45:10,792
那傢夥比海軍陸戰隊員還高2英尺
<font color="#808080">JJ:</font> That thing is like two feet taller than the marine.

723
00:45:10,875 --> 00:45:12,085
太瘋狂了
<font color="#808080">DIMAH:</font> Pretty crazy, huh?

724
00:45:12,168 --> 00:45:14,212
現在看這兒
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Now check this out.

725
00:45:14,295 --> 00:45:16,172
<font color="#D900D9">(gunfire)</font>

726
00:45:16,256 --> 00:45:18,633
小隊，遭遇不明敵軍，撤退
<font color="#808080">MAN:</font> Squad, encountered unknown hostiles. Going back.

727
00:45:19,759 --> 00:45:21,386
噢，怎麼可能！
<font color="#D900D9">(Man screams)</font>

728
00:45:19,759 --> 00:45:21,386
<font color="#808080">JJ:</font> Oh, no way!

729
00:45:21,469 --> 00:45:22,929
你們覺得他們在逃避誰？
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Now, who do you think they're running from?

730
00:45:23,012 --> 00:45:24,889
他們聯手攻擊了麼？
Are they fighting together?

731
00:45:24,973 --> 00:45:26,143
好了，現在到整段的高潮了
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Okay, now here comes the best part.

732
00:45:26,182 --> 00:45:28,351
看，看這兒
Wait, watch... watch this.

733
00:45:28,435 --> 00:45:30,687
那傢夥是什麼？
<font color="#808080">JJ:</font> VVhoa!<font color="#808080"> WALTER:</font> What is that thing?

734
00:45:30,770 --> 00:45:32,522
你們都看到了嗎？
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Do you get this? Are you seeing all this?

735
00:45:37,193 --> 00:45:39,237
現在時間18點整
<font color="#808080">COMPUTER VOICE:</font> It is now 1800.

736
00:45:39,320 --> 00:45:42,031
所有學員去食堂報到
All Cadets report to the Mess Hall.

737
00:45:48,913 --> 00:45:50,957
你覺得那傢夥是什麼？
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> What do you think that thing was?

738
00:45:52,250 --> 00:45:53,626
肯定不是地獄傘兵
<font color="#808080">JJ:</font> Definitely not an ODST.

739
00:45:53,710 --> 00:45:55,295
那他會是什麼？
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Then what could it be?

740
00:45:55,378 --> 00:45:57,797
可能是某種改良版地獄傘兵護甲
<font color="#808080">WALTER:</font> Maybe some upgraded ODST armament.

741
00:45:57,881 --> 00:46:00,008
拜託，你沒瞧見他有多巨大？
<font color="#808080">JJ:</font> Come on, did you not see the size of that thing?

742
00:46:00,091 --> 00:46:01,801
絕不會是地獄傘兵
That's not ODST.

743
00:46:01,885 --> 00:46:04,846
<font color="#D900D9">(imitating gunfire)</font>

744
00:46:05,972 --> 00:46:07,140
各位，你們都沒抓住要點
Guys, look, you're missing the point.

745
00:46:07,223 --> 00:46:11,603
重點是我方士兵和叛軍並肩作戰
What matters is that our soldiers

746
00:46:08,892 --> 00:46:11,603
were fighting alongside the insurrectionists.

747
00:46:11,686 --> 00:46:13,313
我們為何要保護敵軍？
Why would we protect the enemy?

748
00:46:15,482 --> 00:46:17,317
拉斯基學員？
Cadet Lasky?

749
00:46:17,400 --> 00:46:19,527
麥哈非上校要見你
Colonel Mehaffey would like to see you.

750
00:46:28,286 --> 00:46:29,496
你好些了麼？
<font color="#808080">MEHAFFEY:</font> How are you feeling?

751
00:46:31,456 --> 00:46:35,418
我胸還是很痛，長官
My chest burns, sir, quite a bit.

752
00:46:37,962 --> 00:46:39,506
這是給你的
This is for you.

753
00:46:46,763 --> 00:46:49,224
看起來你要做出個決定，托馬斯
Seems like you have a choice to make, Thomas.

754
00:46:53,019 --> 00:46:54,729
我不明白，長官
I don't understand, sir.

755
00:46:55,688 --> 00:46:59,999
看上去休醫生的診斷髮現你對西蒲賽林的
It appears Dr. Hughes' test has revealed

756
00:46:57,899 --> 00:46:59,859
that the level of your allergy to cytoprethaline

757
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:02,862
過敏程度足以批准你因病退伍
is serious enough to warrant a medical discharge.

758
00:47:03,738 --> 00:47:06,324
如果你覺得你不再適合服役
If you feel that you are unfit for service,

759
00:47:06,407 --> 00:47:09,869
你只要在這兒簽字並帶到太空電梯去
all you need to do is sign the release and bring it to the Tether.

760
00:47:16,167 --> 00:47:17,418
我什麼時候會走？
When would I leave?

761
00:47:17,502 --> 00:47:19,671
明天
<font color="#808080">MEHAFFEY:</font> Tomorrow.

762
00:47:20,588 --> 00:47:21,548
明天？
Tomorrow?

763
00:47:21,631 --> 00:47:23,341
你知道的，托馬斯
You know, Thomas,

764
00:47:25,093 --> 00:47:29,180
你留下的將會是你的回憶和決定
your memories and choices are all you'll have left.

765
00:47:31,099 --> 00:47:35,061
遊戲最後，將和卒都會放會棋盒 （不管是偉人還是凡人，死後都會去同樣的地方）
At the end of the game,

766
00:47:32,475 --> 00:47:35,061
the king and the pawn go into the same box.

767
00:47:35,144 --> 00:47:38,648
你必須決定你願意犧牲什麼
You have to decide what you're willing to sacrifice.

768
00:47:48,283 --> 00:47:49,576
Axios
<font color="#808080">MEHAFFEY:</font> <i>Axios.</i>

769
00:47:50,869 --> 00:47:52,412
Axios
<i>Axios.</i>

770
00:47:55,331 --> 00:47:57,542
<font color="#D900D9">(Cadets conversing indistinctly)</font>

771
00:48:22,984 --> 00:48:26,070
托馬斯，我要告訴你一件無比沉痛的事
<font color="#D900D9">(touchscreen beeps)</font>

772
00:48:22,984 --> 00:48:26,070
Thomas, it is with a heavy heart that I must inform you

773
00:48:26,154 --> 00:48:30,700
今天你哥哥凱德蒙在安德西亞被叛軍殺了
that today your brother, Cadmon, was shot down

774
00:48:28,031 --> 00:48:30,700
by insurrectionist forces on Andesia.

775
00:48:30,783 --> 00:48:32,452
他的小隊成員都被殺了
All of his squad perished.

776
00:48:32,535 --> 00:48:35,204
他們死時應該很快，毫無痛苦
I've been told it was a quick and painless death.

777
00:48:35,288 --> 00:48:37,582
沒有遺骸留下
There are no remains to bury.

778
00:48:37,665 --> 00:48:39,292
鑒於此，我決定你
With this in mind, I have decided that you

779
00:48:39,375 --> 00:48:41,502
不應該離開科布羅學院參加葬禮…
shall not leave Corbulo to attend services...

780
00:48:41,586 --> 00:48:45,214
<font color="#D900D9">(Colonel Lasky's voice fades)</font>

781
00:48:45,298 --> 00:48:47,008
<font color="#D900D9">(Inaudible)</font>

782
00:48:54,849 --> 00:48:56,059
拉斯基上校通話完畢
Colonel Lasky out.

783
00:48:56,142 --> 00:48:57,518
拉斯基？
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Lasky?

784
00:48:58,645 --> 00:49:00,313
拉斯基，挪開，我給你看樣東西
Lasky, move over. I gotta show you something.

785
00:49:00,396 --> 00:49:01,648
我不是很方便，小蘇
Now's not a good time, Sully, okay?

786
00:49:01,731 --> 00:49:03,483
這真的很重要
No, it's important.

787
00:49:11,491 --> 00:49:13,576
這他媽的是啥？
<font color="#808080">SULLY:</font> Now what the hell is that?

788
00:49:15,745 --> 00:49:16,829
Hmm?

789
00:49:19,832 --> 00:49:22,502
哇！怎麼回事？
Whoa! Whoa! What...?

790
00:49:22,585 --> 00:49:23,962
離線了
It's offline.

791
00:49:24,045 --> 00:49:26,673
我搞砸了，是海軍情報處幹的
I'm screwed, man. It's ONI.

792
00:49:26,756 --> 00:49:28,424
他們肯定標記了這些影片
They must have flagged those come.

793
00:49:28,508 --> 00:49:30,093
我要去問問迪瑪
I got to talk to Dimah.

794
00:49:30,176 --> 00:49:32,845
迪瑪？你跟你媽說過那事？
Dimah? Did you tell your mom?

795
00:49:35,181 --> 00:49:36,307
凱勒？
Chyler?

796
00:49:51,990 --> 00:49:54,742
<font color="#D900D9">(crickets chirping)</font>

797
00:49:56,160 --> 00:49:57,912
嘿
<font color="#808080">THOMAS:</font> Hey.

798
00:50:03,251 --> 00:50:05,003
我一直都挺想坐坐你這個位子
<font color="#808080">CHYLER:</font> I thought I'd give your spot a try.

799
00:50:07,463 --> 00:50:09,841
那段影片根本說不通
That com didn't make any sense.

800
00:50:09,924 --> 00:50:12,010
我的理解一直是敵人都是可憎的
Hating the looies is all I've ever known.

801
00:50:15,263 --> 00:50:16,931
你跟麥哈非上校說過嗎？
Did you tell Mehaffey about it?

802
00:50:21,227 --> 00:50:22,311
沒
No.

803
00:50:24,355 --> 00:50:26,065
沒有
No.

804
00:50:29,986 --> 00:50:30,987
那是什麼？
What's that?

805
00:50:34,157 --> 00:50:36,784
我顯然是對戰爭過敏
Apparently, I'm allergic to war.

806
00:50:42,957 --> 00:50:44,584
什麼意思？
What does this mean?

807
00:50:44,667 --> 00:50:46,210
你要離開這兒？
You're leaving?

808
00:50:48,463 --> 00:50:50,339
嗯，如果我簽字的話明天就走
Yeah, tomorrow, if I sign it.

809
00:50:50,423 --> 00:50:52,508
你打算簽麼？
Are you going to?

810
00:50:55,470 --> 00:50:56,596
我不知道
I don't know.

811
00:50:59,390 --> 00:51:00,850
凱勒…
Chyler...

812
00:51:00,933 --> 00:51:02,018
沒關係的
It's okay.

813
00:51:03,102 --> 00:51:04,937
我知道你不想待在這兒
I know you don't want to be here.

814
00:51:05,021 --> 00:51:08,149
我只是想也許…
I just thought that maybe...

815
00:51:13,029 --> 00:51:14,906
我會想念你的
I'll miss you.

816
00:51:32,381 --> 00:51:37,428
<font color="#D900D9">(alarm siren sounds)</font>

817
00:51:37,512 --> 00:51:38,513
怎麼回事？
What is that?

818
00:51:39,388 --> 00:51:41,808
所有學員去太空電梯處報到
<font color="#808080">COMPUTER VOICE:</font> All Cadets report to the Tether.

819
00:51:41,891 --> 00:51:43,184
我不知道
I don't know.

820
00:51:43,267 --> 00:51:44,644
全校疏散
<font color="#808080">COMPUTER VOICE:</font> Campus-wide evacuation.

821
00:51:44,727 --> 00:51:46,729
去太空電梯那兒，快！
To the Tether, now!

822
00:51:46,813 --> 00:51:48,689
這不是演習！
This is not a drill!

823
00:51:48,773 --> 00:51:50,858
快！抓緊！
Let's go, let's go, let's go! Come on!

824
00:51:50,942 --> 00:51:52,819
快走！
<font color="#808080">WOMAN:</font> Okay, let's go!

825
00:51:54,278 --> 00:51:57,115
全校疏散
<font color="#808080">COMPUTER VOICE:</font> Full campus evacuation.

826
00:51:57,198 --> 00:51:58,449
全校…
